These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: fishing, reading
There are 2 different nationalities: pakistani, malaysian
1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
2. the malaysian is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Hobby   | reading  | fishing |
| Nationality       | pakistani | malaysian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: house, rock
City: paris, new-york
1. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3
2. the fan of rock is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Music-Genre   | house | rock |
| City      | new-york     | paris  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
City: marseilles, london
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, august
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| City   | marseilles | london  |
| Birthday   | september | august |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, bongani
House: craftsman, tower
1. the craftsman house is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
2. the havana-smoker is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |
| Cigar   | bongani | havana   |
| House       | tower | craftsman |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-5::.
