2 different games are played: monopoly, canasta
1. the person playing canasta is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Pet   | guinea-pig    | chinchilla    |
| Game   | monopoly | canasta |

